{"tid":100742,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人呀媽隔一排就無啦啦會發脾氣","createTime":"2017-01-30T09:40:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-04T17:02:13.000Z","uid":973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4123c3dd33f1fd8b4ab8c8ea04c73c75411a7ac2","tid":100742,"uid":973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T09:40:00.000Z","msg":"R撚哂頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n全日完全無做過d咩，計都無傾兩句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但自己會無啦啦心情勁差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後黑哂面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n完全諗唔到邊度踩親偉大的母親條尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申: 孝順仔"},{"pid":"a7f9170a3904c0a00b23e4df9665bd55481e468d","tid":100742,"uid":973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T09:41:57.000Z","msg":"求其他孝順仔分析<br />\n老母個心究竟諗緊咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"699afb9207584e88df7f2bdbcc443b41fcc85e03","tid":100742,"uid":16395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T09:41:59.000Z","msg":"硬食無誤<br />\n是咪更年期喇？"},{"pid":"3113a415f360c4c719ff1dcfe7a369fd351d1117","tid":100742,"uid":973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T09:46:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>硬食無誤<br />\n是咪更年期喇？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n5x 啦，但仲番緊工<br />\n發脾氣個規律大致上都估到<br />\n同我+老豆一齊放假<br />\n發脾氣機率有90%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n自己放假又唔會<br />\n大時大節發脾氣機率有80%<br />\n<br />\n今日連野食都買埋比佢，佢岩岩番工都無食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b90f33e38edac0b32b346fda89520958b73dc9ac","tid":100742,"uid":973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T09:52:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgm